so i was sitting here today with patty, looking at all our old lj entries n shit. i've come to the conclusion that i don't really know myself. i think i got hollowed out and replaced. i guess that's called growing, but i dunno...i'd rather just think that i'm some sort of like alien robot inhabiting the body of this boring humanoid. humans totally suck. fuck humans, and fuck all y'alls. if i had the energy, i would surely beat you. be-fuckin-ware.

hey, did you guys ever notice how monotonous and kind of boring life here on earth is? because it is. and you oughtta know it. also, cocks.

p.s. i made cooking the other day, it was delicious
well, i wanted to write something, but i was overcome by the lameness of livejournal, sooo...catch you later!

oh well.



i'm looking at all my old entries, and i've come to realized something...leaving school has done me good. i feel like i have a better time expressing myself in writing. i don't know what connection that has to me leaving school, but there's one somewhere. maybe it's just because i read more. if only i understood the art of conversation, then i would REAAlly be able to say i know the english language. i don't have the right to say that at this point. i feel like a foreigner sometimes.


ummm....so i'm really drunk, ok.


two bottles of wine. TWO BOTTLES OF WINE!

actually only one, but who's counting.

i beliiieve in makin it easy


does anyone ever go on this website anymore? i'd almost completely forgot about it. 
here's what's new with me:
1)nothing


the end!

i think i am going to transfer to berkeley high. i need to stop this lonely habit of iscolation! it's so boring! and i just can't take independent study anymore, i can't be trusted to do so much work on my own. mostly because i don't feel the things i'm learning are important for what i want to do with my life.  i just want to be left alone so that i can work on music and art and all the other things that i want to do...but i know i need to get my high school diploma. i need to graduate highschool. do i? i do... i at least need some sort of plan. i do not know! 





i don't fucking know.
i wish all of my stupid new drug and women's classes were taught be nuns. that would be HILARIOUS.

i'm feeling pretty good about school this year. the only problem is, i'm constantly changing my view on it. that's always my problem. but i'm totally hoping that doesn't happen, because the first two days have been almost excellent. almost.

i feel like the whole world is mindfucking me. i must be going crazy. aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaah, strange. i don't even know how to begin to explain.

i am very hungry. ooooooh i'll make a panini!!!!!!! i totally have percuto, however you spell it...that italian ham stuff...and baguette and i don't have mozerella, but i can use cheddar cheese instead. fuck, i can't wait. thank god for food network.

today i woke up, and almost immediatly after that me and bekka modled for bekka's brother and got to dress up in cool clothes and were crazy. then i went to garrett's and it was tweeks birthday and we smoked a blunt. and then we played monopoly, and i had a vicodin so i wouldn't get bored. it didn't really work, but now i'm really tired.

i had a really weird dream last night. as usual. but it was totally scary. i forget the beginning, but somehow garrett/someone else(i forget the other person, but it kept switching between them) got caught in this jail thing, i'm not sure why, but i ran in a helped him escape. and then we raaan and ran and ran and ran, for what seemed like forever, but i really wasn't tired. then garrett ducks into an alley, and we're saved because the cops can't find us in alleys, i guess. then garrett's like "oh, i'm about to go to a party" and i'm like "i wanna go" and i magically have money. then we go to the beach, and there isn't really a party. but there's a convenient store sort of like a resort type of beach. and then i think i walk into the store, but it's actually a house inside. well, not really a house, more just like a hallway. and then like this weird man that is really tall and all in black with black dreads (they somehow seem to fade to blonde by the end), and looking really goth comes, pretty much out of the wall. he imedially like leads me down a staircase and says "let me show you to your room" in a very classy sort of tone. at the end of the staircase are three doors, and he leads me into the second one. it's a really messy room, with a recliner sort of chair in the middle, which he motions me to sit down in. i do. and then he leaves. a few seconds after, an old and very crazy looking lady comes in. she reminds me of a doctor. she says "your tits are too small" and leaves the room. then suddenly i'm in a car, and i don't know how to drive a car. but still, i try driving it, but i'm at an inrersection and i can't find the break. then i stear out of the road and get it under control, right as a police man rolls by. so i get out of my car, and somehow i'm where the party is supposed to be, but it's a beach again. and there's the man with the dreads, and it's his party. i go on the beach, and find a few people smoking cigarettes and drinking something out of capree sun bottles. i sit down, it is the party, i ask to bum a cigarette. someone gives me one, but it's really part of a blunt. and i realize everyone's cigarettes are blunts. and someone hands me a bottle, and it's got some sort of really weird drug name on it, and i drink it...then i look up and there's a bike cop walking up to us. he takes us all to the station, which is right on the beach. and then i woooooooooke the fuck up.

weird

i hate people! i hate them all! i hate all you guys! especially the ones that insult me reeeeally bad and not in a jokey way and then when i get pissed off try to be my friend again. what the hell is up with that, seriously.

fuck you.

i had the scariest dream. it started off with something i can't remember, i was at a friend's house or something, but it was exactly where my house is. then for some reason i was on the side of a highway (i think i was trying to get home) and i see this guy kind of dressed up like a woman, and kind of dressed up like a clown. like divine, except really short and ugly, he was really fat, and i liked his fishnet stockings...anyways, i started talking to him and he's just some crossdressing bum, and that gives me an idea. i'll take him to my friend's house for some stupid reason that i don't know at all!! yeah, so then we're at my friend's house and we're waiting for SOMETHING, i'm not sure what, and keeps trying to touch me. he was super fight, so i couldn't really fight back, but i end up knocking him out and fleaing the house. later, i realize that i left all my belongings in the house and i go back, expecting the strange man to be gone...BUT NO, he's in the exact same place, cept naked, with a naked girl, and they're fucking eachother with knives. eeew, it was so gross, and the guy now looked like the penguin from batman. they somehow capture me, and i don't remember what happened after that, but it was a lot of shit fucking with my mind n stuff. eventually there were more people, and the house gets bigger, and they pretty much take it over. at this point i'm sooo scared, and i decide i should get the police into it. as i'm calling 911, for some reason i think to my self "my mom is going to kill me for getting the police into this". almost imediatly "911" answers, and instead of a nice po po man it's my mom, and she starts making fun of me "oh! we're here! were gonna save you, xeena!" and i'm like "mom, this is serious, they almost just cut off my finger, i'm gonna diiiie!!!!!!!!" i don't remember what the rest of the conversation was like, but she came over to the house. i hear the doorbell, and i grab everything i have, at this point i think i'm naked, about to go running in the san pablo streets at whatever late time it was...anywho i answer the door and my mom's all highspirited and says are you ready to go? and i look over to where her car was parked...and it wasn't there...they had stolen it in a few seconds and now we're trapped, and we start freaking out..................and then i finally fucking woke up. yaay!

that didn't make any sense, i'm sorry.

i had the most shitty and uncomfortable two days of my life. i ran away, and was gonna sell my guitar and run far away if they gave me enough money for it...but they were only gonna give me 30 bucks, so instead i sat on a corner crying for a little bit and thinking about how if i don't get the fuck out of here i am going to go crazy and just not do anything. i'm still so scared that that's where i'm headed. i talked to my mom, and she pretty much agrees that i need to get out of berkeley. but yeah, i came home and basically cried for five hours straight, and then woke up in the morning and cried for another hour. i'm just going insane. i don't have anyone to open up to. i also don't have any motivation. that's why i need to get out on my own. i need to be forced to do something with my life.

in other news, my cat has fleas, and that makes me even more pissed off.

i always feel like people are talking about me. it never used to happen before, but now it's getting a little crazy. i guess i'm getting really insecure in myself or something. it's terrible. it haunts meeeeeeee. everytime i can't hear what two people are whispering about, i hear my name. every time i'm away from a situation, i'm thinking "oh blah blah blah happened a little while ago, and now they're talking about how stupid i am." it's just...ridonkulous.

she comes to my house every once in a while and hears my mom and me get in fights, she's somehow tied to carry that on into mine and her relationship as she is taking care of me. she's not my fucking mother! i can hardly deal with my mother! AAAAAAAAAAGHHHHHHHHHHH
